				\begin{document}$$\begin{array}{c}MR=\frac{{M}_{\tau }-{M}_{\mathrm{e}}}{{M}_{0}-{M}_{\mathrm{e}}}=4{\sum }_{n=1}^{\infty }\frac{1}{{B}_{n}^{2}}exp(-{B}_{n}^{2}\frac{{D}_{eff}\tau }{{L}^{2}})\end{array}$$\end{document}where Deff is the effective moisture diffusivity, m2/s; Bn is the root of the zero order Bessel function.

